Welcome to the Cone Finder app

This app is created and designed in order to annotate foveal images and make some simple analysis.
Table of Contents
Main features Disclaimer Cites

Main features

  • Cone detection by neural network.
  • Manual annotation of the cones.
  • Different representation of the cones over the foveal image.
  • Import/Export data by csv files.
  • Calculation of basic analysis like density map, CDC, PCD and thier representation.
